5
00:00:18,218 --> 00:00:23,757
{\an8}KANSAI JOHNNY'S JR.

6
00:00:24,457 --> 00:00:26,860
{\an8}<i>They are all the rage
in the Kansai region,</i>

7
00:00:27,227 --> 00:00:28,828
{\an8}<i>Kansai Johnny's Jr.</i>

8
00:00:31,531 --> 00:00:34,434
<i>They may not be well-known
on a national level yet,</i>

9
00:00:34,834 --> 00:00:37,937
