OSAKA

19
00:01:28,655 --> 00:01:33,860
<i>It's not an easy feat to become
a national idol group from Osaka.</i>

20
00:01:37,931 --> 00:01:40,133
{\an8}<i>In 2004, Kanjani∞ debuted,</i>

21
