27
00:02:03,823 --> 00:02:07,594
<i>They were quietly reaffirming
their determination to debut.</i>

28
00:02:11,397 --> 00:02:14,834
{\an8}The creation of Naniwa Danshi
was a breath of fresh air.

29
00:02:14,901 --> 00:02:15,735
{\an8}DAIGO NISHIHATA (AGE 22)

30
00:02:15,802 --> 00:02:18,304
{\an8}We can show a different side
of Kansai Johnny's Jr.

31
00:02:21,307 --> 00:02:23,476
{\an8}<i>At the end of the year
they'll be performing...</i>

32
00:02:24,878 --> 00:02:27,480
{\an8}<i>at the legendary Osaka Shochikuza Theatre.</i>

33
00:02:27,547 --> 00:02:30,550
{\an8}OSAKA SHOCHIKUZA THEATRE
1 MONTH, 35 PERFORMANCES

34
00:02:31,384 --> 00:02:32,785
{\an8}<i>Then at the start of the new year,</i>

35
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:35,255
{\an8}<i>they'll be at Osaka-Jo Hall
for two consecutive days.</i>

36
00:02:35,755 --> 00:02:38,925
{\an8}<i>They will entertain approximately
100,000 people in total.</i>

37
00:02:38,992 --> 00:02:41,294
{\an8}OSAKA-JO HALL
2 DAYS, 4 PERFORMANCES

38
00:02:44,164 --> 00:02:47,433
{\an8}<i>A total of about 50 members
from Kansai Johnny's Jr.</i>

39
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:50,069
{\an8}<i>will perform with them this time.</i>

40
00:02:56,242 --> 00:02:59,012
<i>Singing and dancing
are not all they have going for them.</i>

41
