<i>and others to comedy.</i>

43
00:03:14,394 --> 00:03:16,296
A large knife!

44
00:03:17,797 --> 00:03:19,032
Not a large knife.

45
00:03:20,934 --> 00:03:23,870
<i>Among them are innocent
elementary school kids.</i>

46
00:03:24,737 --> 00:03:25,705
Hyokkori-han.

47
00:03:26,606 --> 00:03:27,640
I'm ten years old.

48
00:03:28,141 --> 00:03:29,075
I'm nine years old.

49
00:03:29,676 --> 00:03:30,510
It died.

50
00:03:30,743 --> 00:03:33,479
<i>As a team,
they stand on stage as professionals.</i>

51
00:03:34,214 --> 00:03:36,983
<i>And that is why they go through
strict training.</i>

52
00:03:37,917 --> 00:03:40,220
-You have to practice.
-Yes.

53
00:03:40,286 --> 00:03:42,422
This is bad. If you can't memorize it,

54
00:03:42,488 --> 00:03:44,424
