55
00:03:44,490 --> 00:03:45,325
Yes.

56
00:03:45,391 --> 00:03:46,359
Let's work hard.

57
00:03:48,127 --> 00:03:51,297
<i>This time, they have
some reliable helpers.</i>

58
00:03:52,999 --> 00:03:57,270
{\an8}<i>Their seniors from Kansai Johnny's Jr.,
Kanjani∞'s Tadayoshi Ohkura</i>

59
00:03:57,337 --> 00:04:01,708
{\an8}<i>and You Yokoyama, have volunteered
to direct the composition and production.</i>

60
00:04:02,575 --> 00:04:05,478
