61
00:04:05,545 --> 00:04:10,216
but there are so many more
amazing talents here.

62
00:04:11,017 --> 00:04:13,319
Thinking about what we can do

63
00:04:13,820 --> 00:04:16,856
to make those talents shine

64
00:04:16,923 --> 00:04:19,459
is our job right now, I think.

65
00:04:21,594 --> 00:04:25,465
<i>Will they succeed at
having the performance of their dreams?</i>

66
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:31,671
Nice to meet you!
We are Kansai Johnny's Jr.!

67
00:04:32,071 --> 00:04:33,072
Viva!

68
00:04:40,613 --> 00:04:42,081
{\an8}NOVEMBER 2018
OSAKA

69
00:04:42,148 --> 00:04:44,984
{\an8}<i>It's early November,
and their first day of rehearsals.</i>

70
00:04:47,253 --> 00:04:48,354
-Morning.
-Morning.

71
00:04:48,521 --> 00:04:51,958
<i>As we film the members walking in...</i>

72
00:04:53,626 --> 00:04:54,594
<i>all of a sudden...</i>

73
00:04:55,495 --> 00:04:56,696
{\an8}I'll do a party stunt!

74
00:04:56,763 --> 00:04:59,499
{\an8}I'll make a kanji character with my body.

75
