00:14:09,081 --> 00:14:11,050
No, that's no good. It's too fast.

234
00:14:11,717 --> 00:14:14,253
We danced behind
the younger generations too.

235
00:14:14,753 --> 00:14:15,721
-Really?
-Yes.

236
00:14:16,689 --> 00:14:17,523
Right?

237
00:14:18,123 --> 00:14:20,392
I was a backup dancer for WEST.

238
00:14:20,459 --> 00:14:21,694
For Johnny's WEST?

239
00:14:22,194 --> 00:14:23,195
They're younger?

240
00:14:23,262 --> 00:14:24,129
A few of them.

241
00:14:24,463 --> 00:14:25,598
That's how it is here.

242
00:14:26,498 --> 00:14:27,533
Understood.

243
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:28,667
It doesn't matter.

244
00:14:28,734 --> 00:14:29,802
That's right.

245
00:14:29,869 --> 00:14:31,070
<i>It's a tough world.</i>

246
00:14:32,471 --> 00:14:35,441
<i>But despite that fact,
