336
00:21:54,846 --> 00:21:55,681
Okay.

337
00:21:56,481 --> 00:21:57,416
What about...

338
00:21:57,683 --> 00:21:58,717
It's here.

339
00:21:59,084 --> 00:22:01,320
<i>Naniwa Danshi's opponent...</i>

340
00:22:03,021 --> 00:22:04,890
Hey, wait a second!

341
00:22:06,958 --> 00:22:09,828
<i>...is a group of unique individuals
led by Mukai.</i>

342
00:22:09,895 --> 00:22:12,197
-It has to be us.
