344
00:22:16,935 --> 00:22:18,470
Is that supposed to be cool?

345
00:22:19,104 --> 00:22:23,075
Let me grace you with a cool phrase.

346
00:22:24,609 --> 00:22:26,011
Can you?

347
00:22:26,078 --> 00:22:29,114
